          <p class="title is-3"><a href="/2019/implicit-ethics.html" class="has-text-primary">Neue Publikation: Implicit Ethics</a></p>
          <p class="subtitle is-5">Normative Claims to Culture in Multilateral Negotiations</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="columns">
        <div class="column is-3 is-hidden-touch ">
<div class="is-size-7 has-text-black">SchlagwÃ¶rter:<br /><span class="has-text-link">Aktuelles<br />Publikationen<br />Artikel<br />Peer Reviewed</span></div>
<div class="is-size-7 has-text-black"><br />Links:<br /><a href="https://anthrosource.onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/full/10.1111/jola.12258" class="has-text-primary">Paper auf AnthroSource</a><br /><a href="https://anthrosource.onlinelibrary.wiley.com/journal/15481395" class="has-text-primary">Journal auf AnthroSource</a></div>

